  * [Spies Without Borders Series: Using Domestic Networks to Spy on the World](https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2013/06/spy-without-borders) – Electronic Frontier Foundation

  * [Online Survival Kit for Journalists](https://www.wefightcensorship.org/online-survival-kithtml.html) – Reporters Without Borders

